Privacy Policy for Game Dev Story on Apple Arcade
Last Updated: April 20, 2021
◆ Introduction
Kairosoft Co., Ltd. (referred to as "our company") will strive to respect the privacy of customers and protect personal information in accordance with the following policies.
■ Compliance with laws and regulations
We will comply with laws and other relevant laws concerning the protection of personal information about the acquisition, use and other handling of personal information.
■ Data collected
We do not collect, process or store any personal data from our games on Apple Arcade. We don’t use any in-app purchases and we don’t place any advertisements in our games on Apple Arcade. We do not store personal or gameplay data on our servers.
Our games collect non-personal data using integrated Apple services for cloud saves using Apple iCloud and collect non-personal, anonymized, aggregated data for Apple App Analytics for the purpose of analytics.
All uses of Apple Arcade are subject to Apple Arcade’s Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of Apple or its third parties partners.
You may decline to store data in the iCloud. To turn off iCloud data storage, you must turn off iCloud in Apple Settings for our game.
■ Application
This Privacy Policy and the collection, provision and storage of the Data shall be applied to all users of the Service.
By playing our games on Apple Arcade, you acknowledge that you have read and understand the terms of this Privacy Policy.
■ About change
We may change the purpose of use and other contents of this privacy policy without prior notice.If there is any change, we will make it public on our website.
■ Inquiries
For inquiries concerning the handling of personal information by our company, you may contact us using the information below.
